  {"id":"ntpc-m-0001","correctOption":"B","difficulty":"easy","sourceYear":2024,"en":{"question":"The area of a square is 196 sq cm. What is the length of its diagonal?","options":["14 cm","14√2 cm","28 cm","7√2 cm"],"explanation":"Side = √196 = 14 cm. Diagonal = side × √2 = 14√2 cm."},"hi":{"question":"वर्ग का क्षेत्रफल 196 वर्ग सेमी। विकर्ण की लंबाई?","options":["14 सेमी","14√2 सेमी","28 सेमी","7√2 सेमी"],"explanation":"भुजा=14, विकर्ण=14√2 सेमी।"}},
  {"id":"ntpc-m-0002","correctOption":"A","difficulty":"medium","sourceYear":2023,"en":{"question":"A cylindrical tank has radius 7m and height 10m. What is its capacity in kiloliters? (Take π = 22/7)","options":["1540 kL","154 kL","2200 kL","3080 kL"],"explanation":"Volume = πr²h = (22/7)×49×10 = 1540 m³ = 1540 kL."},"hi":{"question":"बेलनाकार टंकी, त्रिज्या 7m, ऊँचाई 10m। क्षमता (kL में)?","options":["1540 kL","154 kL","2200 kL","3080 kL"],"explanation":"आयतन=(22/7)×49×10=1540 m³=1540 kL।"}},
